{"id":"811076801593016320","type":"text","timestamp":1773503114,"post_url":"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/goodtransgirl/811076801593016320","is_reblog":true,"added_content":false,"tags":[],"reblog_ready":false,"body":"<p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/witchofthebloodleaftome/811076092276424704\">witchofthebloodleaftome</a>:</p><blockquote><p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://cholerascum.tumblr.com/post/811075884655280128/theres-an-inherent-sisterhood-between-all-trans\">cholerascum</a>:</p><blockquote><p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/nekomimidusteon/810564638107484164\">nekomimidusteon</a>:</p><blockquote><p>one of the slightly less talked about benefits of transitioning is you get so many new sisters</p></blockquote><p>there&rsquo;s an inherent sisterhood between all trans women and I&rsquo;ll die on this hill.</p></blockquote><p>Oh my Spirits that&rsquo;s so true mew X3 <a class=\"tumblelog\" href=\"https://tmblr.co/MsAzk9kb8dfc8RNDB2qzR_g\">@goodtransgirl</a> @gwendolyn_of_loxley <a class=\"tumblelog\" href=\"https://tmblr.co/M812zLWp3pVuUOAcUCXG-dg\">@snout2snout</a> </p></blockquote>","trail":[{"blog":{"name":"nekomimidusteon"},"post":{"id":"810564638107484164"}},{"blog":{"name":"cholerascum"},"post":{"id":"811075884655280128"}},{"blog":{"name":"witchofthebloodleaftome"},"post":{"id":"811076092276424704"}}],"baseline_notes":1738,"baseline_ts":1774705101.464}